  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served every morning with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner is three courses with a choice of local and international dishes on offer in one of the hotel's two restaurants, which are full of character and art.</p>
<p>This restaurants have a vibrant feel to them and are also open to the public. The hotel is well known for it's great quality food and is a very popular place to eat. They also have a fantastic wine selection which will make your dinner experience even better! </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year Gala dinners are included (24th and 31st December).</p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <deactivateThisPage>0</deactivateThisPage>
  <description><![CDATA[<p>If you're looking for something a little different for your next ski holiday, Hotel Grivola is a great choice. With its location in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bfccaf52eb4c47f09ae3657298234fda}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, you'll have everything you need on your doorstep and the ski lifts are only 100 metres away. </p>
<h2>Unique Art Hotel</h2>
<p>Throughout the property you'll find a range of work by artist Gabriele Maquignaz. There's abstract art hanging on the walls and beautiful sculptures dotted about the place. Literally everywhere you look there's something to admire and we love the quirkiness throughout. </p>
<h2>Comfy Surroundings</h2>
<p>The rooms are really comfy and they have pretty much everything you need for an great stay. The spa has a warming sauna to soothe out any aches or pains, just book on arrival.</p>
<h2>Dining</h2>
<p>Enjoy a drink at the bar before indulging in some local and international dishes served in the restaurant. Be sure to check out the wine list too, there's some great labels in the cellar.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Grivola the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
